            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p><strong>Once</strong> the chicken has had 15 min oven-time, remove the dish from the oven and place the mozzarella slices over each piece of chicken</p>\r\n<p><strong>Sprinkle</strong> the remaining oregano over the mozzarella slices</p>\r\n<p><strong>Put</strong> the dish back into the oven for 5 min or until the mozzarella has melted and the chicken is cooked through</p>",
